<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p align="center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200901/ca6de8aafa714b459029c01264474420.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">童书推广人菠菠开展亲子绘本故事会</p>
